Third Department,

September, 1946.

(September 11, 1946.) Harry G. Eckert, Respondent, v. City of New York, Appellant. (Action No. 1.) Ira E. Terry, Appellant, v. City of New York, Respondent. (Action No. 2.)

—Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals in action of Harry G. Eckert v. City of New York denied, without costs. All concur. [See 270 App. Div. 642.]
